@startuml
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

title WallRunner v3.0 — 物理引擎子系统类图

package "com.wallrunner.shared.physics" {
    interface IPhysicsEngine {
        +initState(GameState): void
        +update(GameState): void
        +handleInput(Player, String): void
        +startGame(GameState): void
        +initJoiningPlayer(GameState, Player): void
    }

    class PhysicsEngine implements IPhysicsEngine {
        -movementSystem: IMovementSystem
        -collisionDetector: ICollisionDetector
        -obstacleManager: IObstacleManager
        -collectibleManager: ICollectibleManager
        -cameraSystem: ICameraSystem
        -knockbackSystem: IKnockbackSystem
        -invincibilitySystem: IInvincibilitySystem
        -deathSystem: IDeathSystem
        -scoreCalculator: IScoreCalculator
        -difficultyManager: IDifficultyManager
        -playerCollisionResolver: IPlayerCollisionResolver
        -inputHandler: IInputHandler
        -eventBus: GameEventBus
        +createDefault(GameEventBus): PhysicsEngine
    }

    class GamePhysics {
        -ENGINE: IPhysicsEngine
        +initState(GameState): void
        +update(GameState): void
        +handleInput(Player, String): void
        +startGame(GameState): void
        +initJoiningPlayer(GameState, Player): void
    }
}

package "com.wallrunner.shared.physics.subsystem" {
    interface IMovementSystem
    interface ICollisionDetector
    interface IObstacleManager
    interface ICollectibleManager
    interface ICameraSystem
    interface IKnockbackSystem
    interface IInvincibilitySystem
    interface IDeathSystem
    interface IScoreCalculator
    interface IDifficultyManager
    interface IPlayerCollisionResolver
    interface IInputHandler

    class CollisionSystem implements ICollisionDetector
    class MovementSystem implements IMovementSystem
    class ObstacleManager implements IObstacleManager
    class CollectibleManager implements ICollectibleManager
    class CameraSystem implements ICameraSystem
    class KnockbackSystem implements IKnockbackSystem
    class InvincibilitySystem implements IInvincibilitySystem
    class DeathSystem implements IDeathSystem
    class ScoreSystem implements IScoreCalculator
    class DifficultyManager implements IDifficultyManager
    class PlayerCollisionResolver implements IPlayerCollisionResolver
    class InputHandler implements IInputHandler
}

IPhysicsEngine <|.. PhysicsEngine
PhysicsEngine --> IMovementSystem : uses
PhysicsEngine --> ICollisionDetector : uses
PhysicsEngine --> IObstacleManager : uses
PhysicsEngine --> ICollectibleManager : uses
PhysicsEngine --> ICameraSystem : uses
PhysicsEngine --> IKnockbackSystem : uses
PhysicsEngine --> IInvincibilitySystem : uses
PhysicsEngine --> IDeathSystem : uses
PhysicsEngine --> IScoreCalculator : uses
PhysicsEngine --> IDifficultyManager : uses
PhysicsEngine --> IPlayerCollisionResolver : uses
PhysicsEngine --> IInputHandler : uses

GamePhysics ..> PhysicsEngine : delegates

note right of PhysicsEngine
  Facade + 组合模式
  12个子系统通过接口解耦
end note

note right of GamePhysics
  兼容门面（Facade）
  向后兼容v2.0调用方
  @deprecated
end note
@enduml
